  "detailed_description": "<h1>关于我们</h1><p><strong><u>玩家群：894964809（供玩家交流ww遇到种问题也可以来反馈！）<br>游戏开发者微博：@符绾_Retsu<br><br>可以点击上方【发行商】一栏，进入我们的主页。<br>关注我们，即可获取更多后续游戏相关消息哦~</u></strong></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/8038595b4a4833afb9393f31a5ef9d8e.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=84 /></span><br>居住在极北之地的少女瑟里卡，每晚都会在睡梦中进入另一个世界——<br>这里有着她未曾见过的风景，鲜活的友人，以及一场奇迹般的邂逅。<br>懵懂的感情为之觉醒，却被提醒一切只是幻梦……<br>梦与现实究竟有什么联系，她们的命运又会发生怎样的转变呢？<br>迷雾笼罩身周，她将舒展梦境的羽翼，为黎明献上歌唱。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/c202fb9a64603275743b7f917ea09078.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=790 /></span><br>这是一款较为轻松的剧情向解谜游戏，你将扮演瑟里卡在这个世界中度过新年前的七天。<br>你需要翻越雪山、穿过森林，也会遇到一些阻碍。<br>本作游戏时长约为8~10小时，共有三个结局。<br>请拨开纠缠的迷雾，寻找世界的真相吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/299a965da9c27b398b438cfcd2b0b48b.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/d29179384645e0ae28811256d677ed10.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=400 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/28d2b748e0b2faf0970b1000943d7c5a.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=400 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/4119b1a1aba93b9c9d4f61b28b79969c.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=400 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/c93b928cb145e53ef15de44a5edfd59c.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=340 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/c0c14b83c56e365d426f40b76f29f40a.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=84 /></span><br>使用鼠标或方向键进行移动<br>空格/z/Enter 确认/进行调查<br>Esc/x 取消/打开菜单<br><br>※地图上有一些可收集物，把它们送给合适的人，可以了解到更多的信息。<br>※试试仔细观察地图，也许有一些线索帮助你找到前进的道路。<br>※遇到卫兵的搜查记得及时存档，被他们抓到可不是什么好事情。<br><br>部分玩法内容预览：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/13f6c5f03ff2ad0b3f134adb09137fe9.poster.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/13f6c5f03ff2ad0b3f134adb09137fe9.webm?t=1698129487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/13f6c5f03ff2ad0b3f134adb09137fe9.mp4?t=1698129487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/38e7f80525ea8c80b1978ca4db997325.poster.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/38e7f80525ea8c80b1978ca4db997325.webm?t=1698129487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/38e7f80525ea8c80b1978ca4db997325.mp4?t=1698129487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875140/extras/eda89a7ca0e4294d698b7d21b70318c6.poster.avif?t=1698129487\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steams